703384f-a.title: Brooklyn: Bush Street - Hicks Street
703384f-a.text:
97-135 Bush Street, north side, from Hicks to Henry Streets. as viewed
across 1ots from Lorraine Street. The view shows one of the H.C. Bohack
chain of grocery stores at the corner.
June 25, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
